ClusterControllerClient doesn&#39;t have a main.  Its an interface: 
http://crawler.archive.org/hcc/xref/org/archive/hcc/client/ClusterControllerClient.html 
(Neither does the implementation have a main).

It looks like the expectation is that you instantiate a CCC in your 
code.  There is an example in the hcc javadoc overview: 
http://crawler.archive.org/hcc/apidocs/index.html.

Regards client command descriptions, check out the javadoc for CCC: 
http://crawler.archive.org/hcc/apidocs/org/archive/hcc/client/ClusterControllerClient.html.

